  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1681365087\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Domino Galaxy is a minimalist puzzle that uses domino pieces combined with a galaxy theme to promote a unique, enjoyable and relaxing atmosphere. Arrange the dominoes to connect like numbers and form a complete sequence, while basking at the dazzling stars of the universe.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2>Change the dominoes positions...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/34eded192afc44a6c2a36ad5a7b966f2.poster.avif?t=1681365087\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/34eded192afc44a6c2a36ad5a7b966f2.webm?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/34eded192afc44a6c2a36ad5a7b966f2.mp4?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Spin the dominoes...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/4aaffbdea3b9b6280336c7336b301f55.poster.avif?t=1681365087\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/4aaffbdea3b9b6280336c7336b301f55.webm?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/4aaffbdea3b9b6280336c7336b301f55.mp4?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And form the correct sequence to win!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/4eadd54873d617c85ece9b3e3884469f.poster.avif?t=1681365087\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/4eadd54873d617c85ece9b3e3884469f.webm?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271040/extras/4eadd54873d617c85ece9b3e3884469f.mp4?t=1681365087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 difficulty modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 7 domino's - 50 Levels<br></li><li> 14 domino's - 50 Levels<br></li><li> 21 domino's - 50 Levels<br></li><li> 28 domino's - 50 Levels</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Resources</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Relaxing and immersive music<br></li><li> Minimalist art<br></li><li> Steam Cloud and Steam Achievements</li></ul>",
